      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to an impeccable standard that mirrors its original showroom delivery. This motorcar has been curated for the discerning enthusiast, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in pristine, untouched condition. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance and presentation. This is an assertive choice for those who demand uncompromising quality and a vehicle that stands as a benchmark for its model year.",
