    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty to believe it\u2014it\u2019s in absolutely stunning condition and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. It\u2019s super clean inside and out, and I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to get behind the wheel. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
