      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, reflecting a standard of preservation rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously maintained interior, demonstrates an uncompromising commitment to care. Mechanically beyond reproach, this vehicle offers a driving experience indistinguishable from its original debut. We invite discerning collectors and enthusiasts to inspect this peerless offering.",
      "price": 44900.0,
