    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s been kept in pristine condition inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to message me if you want to come take a look!",
