    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54 platform, maintaining factory tolerances across all critical systems. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six exhibits perfect compression and leak-down results, with the high-pressure Vanos system recently serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The chassis remains structurally flawless, featuring a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common floor pan fatigue. Power is delivered through a crisp six-speed manual gearbox to a factory-spec limited-slip differential, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. Finished in collector-grade condition with zero oxidation on the underside components, this vehicle represents a turnkey investment for the discerning purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
